descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Avanti’s, Central Illinois most award winning group of Italian restaurants. It is our desire to continue serving you, our highly valued customers with great Italian food, great times and great prices as we have since 1966. We invite you to browse our site and check out the five Avanti’s locations, and the wonderful variety of Italian food all made from our own delicious recipes. As you will see we offer dine-in, carry out and delivery options along with banquet facilities and catering for groups of any size. Thank you for this opportunity to serve you.

Now you can browse our menu and securely place your order from your mobile device! Download and get started today!
